author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-First Commonwealth Bank Announces Pricing Of Subordinated Notes Offerings
text:
May 16 (Reuters) - First Commonwealth Financial Corp :
* FIRST COMMONWEALTH BANK ANNOUNCES PRICING OF SUBORDINATED NOTES OFFERINGS
* FIRST COMMONWEALTH FINANCIAL- FIRST COMMONWEALTH BANK PRICED PRIVATE OFFERING OF $50 MILLION OF ITS 4.875% FIXED-TO-FLOATING RATE SUBORDINATED NOTES DUE 2028
* FIRST COMMONWEALTH FINANCIAL- FIRST COMMONWEALTH BANK PRICED PRIVATE OFFERING OF $50 MILLION OF ITS 5.500% FIXED-TO-FLOATING RATE SUBORDINATED NOTES DUE 2033 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
